{"tid":1254181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】外交部：中國不允許G20峰會討論香港 ","createTime":"2019-06-24T03:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:43:46.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"91f2d4d9093470173bdbc0abad0710608bd432c2","tid":1254181,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"日本大阪G20峰會本周舉行在即，外交部今日（24日）早上舉行中外媒體吹風會。其間，外交部長助理張軍表示，G20峰會不會討論香港議題，中國對此也不允許。<br />\n<br />\n張軍強調，港府修訂《逃犯條例》等一系列舉措，是維護社會公義，彌補法律制度缺陷，是完全有必要的，中央政府也會支持。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">張軍重申，香港是中國的特別行政區，香港事務純屬中國內政，任何國家無權干預。</span><br />\n民陣早前曾號召市民，在G20峰會本月28至29日（周五至周六）舉行前，於周三（26日）晚上8至9時在中環愛丁堡廣場集會，希望藉國際壓力「再給予林鄭月娥重重一擊」。"},{"pid":"4b8c7cd49ecc736174a412c7b990f58a7ccaed4e","tid":1254181,"uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf61f0b4940d71fa61f9bd20c1951122b49eac6b","tid":1254181,"uid":213217,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"咁唔好講華為，人地國家市場，不能干涉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b612e2a6706edd35373c18a635d6ac006edbe8","tid":1254181,"uid":114976,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"干預國際事務？"},{"pid":"7729fe9765ef422bbb2722ce1d7edad9795e644a","tid":1254181,"uid":103759,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"中共驚到腳仔軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁更加要講"},{"pid":"0ed050caf267f93c5e0f304029b45d05fb3492e0","tid":1254181,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"好大既官威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea04f64e75fdd4e239850e001e84c375262c3a7","